lead_paragraph: World Cup-winning fly-half Joel Stransky was less than optimistic about South Africa's chances for their upcoming November internationals against England, Italy and Wales, saying the national side is a "very average" team.

headline.print_headline: Stransky Expects Touring Springboks to 'Suffer Defeats'
headline.main: Stransky Expects Touring Springboks to 'Suffer Defeats'
